interact with each other,

00:02:58.311 --> 00:03:01.114 align:middle line:84%
it becomes what is
called entangled,

00:03:01.114 --> 00:03:04.384 align:middle line:84%
developing a special connected
relationship with one another.

00:03:04.384 --> 00:03:08.421 align:middle line:84%
Now, when one of these particles
are affected say by measurement

00:03:08.421 --> 00:03:12.859 align:middle line:84%
or observation, one particle
will reflect the exact same

00:03:12.859 --> 00:03:16.162 align:middle line:84%
trait as the other
spontaneously.

00:03:16.162 --> 00:03:19.499 align:middle line:84%
No matter how far apart
they are across the room

00:03:19.499 --> 00:03:20.533 align:middle line:90%
or across the universe.

00:03:20.533 --> 00:03:23.470 align:middle line:90%
Einstein found this so strange

00:03:23.470 --> 00:03:30.143 align:middle line:84%
that he later termed it
spooky action at a distance.

00:03:30.143 --> 00:03:32.812 align:middle line:84%
>> Regina: So there's our
spooky action at a distance.

00:03:32.812 --> 00:03:34.748 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to go ahead
and put a definition

00:03:34.748 --> 00:03:36.783 align:middle line:90%
that you have in the book here.

00:03:36.783 --> 00:03:41.153 align:middle line:84%
One mind is like an invisible
non-physical cloud computing

00:03:41.153 --> 00:03:45.458 align:middle line:84%
platform with infinite storage
capacity and is user free.

00:03:45.458 --> 00:03:49.129 align:middle line:84%
